		<title>Source - Redefining WiFi</title>
</head>

<body>
	<%- include('../partials/navbar', { active: 'become-a-host' }) %>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="pure-g">
			<div id="filler1" class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-4-24"></div>
			<div id="red" class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-11-24">
				<div class="img-container">
					<img src="/assets/become-a-host/wifi.png" alt="A Source wifi router">
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="blue" class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-9-24">
				<h2 class="title-2">Share your WiFi and make money doing it.</h2>
				<div class="center-text-sm">
					<!-- TODO (dillchen): Point this URL to the correct page -->
					<p>It’s the same cost as existing routers, and allows you to instantly become a Source Host. If you’re in one of our launch cities, we can even install it for you!</p>
					<a href="/buy" class="button blue-button">Buy Source Router</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

<!---
	<section class="ribbon">
		<p>Own a business and interested in being a host? <a href="/business">Learn more here</a></p>
	</section>
-->

	<section class="share-and-extend">
		<div class="pure-g">
			<%- include('../partials/simpleTwoColumnImageLayout', {
				title: 'Share WiFi with your community.',
				text: 'We let you share your device’s internet access to anyone nearby. People around you get internet access at prices 3x cheaper than mobile data.',
				imageSource: '/assets/become-a-host/houses-icon.png',
				imageAlt: 'A wifi connected house',
			})%>
			<%- include('../partials/simpleTwoColumnImageLayout', {
				title: 'Extend the range of your home wifi. ',
				text: 'While we love our furnishing, decorations, and neighbors, don’t let them hinder your WiFi range. When you add a Source, you make internet access everywhere in your home. ',
				imageSource: '/assets/become-a-host/bed-icon.png',
				imageAlt: 'A furnished room with a bed',
			})%>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="specifications">
		<div class="pure-g">
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
				<img class="router-image" src="/assets/become-a-host/WifiRouter2.png" alt="A source wifi router" />
			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
				<h3>Enables up to 300 MB/S</h3>
				<p>That’s enough for you, your brother, your next door neighbor, and four other people to all be streaming high def videos all day long.</p>
				<img class="spacer-line" src="/assets/become-a-host/gray-line.svg" alt="" />

				<h3>Broadcasts on 802.11n 2.4Ghz and 5Ghz</h3>
				<p>It’s the protocol that allows for the fastests speeds. You never have to compromise on that when you connect.</p>
				<img class="spacer-line" src="/assets/become-a-host/gray-line.svg" alt="" />

				<h3>OpenWRT</h3>
				<p>It runs on an OpenWRT operating system.</p>
				<img class="spacer-line" src="/assets/become-a-host/gray-line.svg" alt="" />

				<h3>17,000 square feet of coverage</h3>
				<p>A standard suburban home lot is about 7,000 square feet, so you can expect a lot of coverage.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="admin-panel">
		<img class="hidden-large-screens small-screen-dashboard" src="/assets/become-a-host/dashboard_view_full.png" alt="The Source admin panel" />			
		<div class="content-container">
			<h3>Stay on top of all the action right through your phone and browser. Manage data, control remotely, and more.</h3>
			<%- include('../partials/xsmallImageBullet', {
				text: 'Automatically paired and recognized by your Source app.',
				imageSource: '/assets/become-a-host/phone.svg',
				imageAlt: 'a phone',
			})%>
			<%- include('../partials/xsmallImageBullet', {
				text: 'You can trust that they aren’t viewing anything they shouldn’t be.',
				imageSource: '/assets/become-a-host/eye.svg',
				imageAlt: 'an eye',
			})%>
			<%- include('../partials/xsmallImageBullet', {
				text: 'You can trust that your own internet experience won’t be slowed down, because we treat your devices with care.',
				imageSource: '/assets/become-a-host/watch.svg',
				imageAlt: 'a watch face',
			})%>
			<%- include('../partials/xsmallImageBullet', {
				text: 'Instantly cash in and out.',
				imageSource: '/assets/become-a-host/safe.svg',
				imageAlt: 'a safe',
			})%>
			<%- include('../partials/xsmallImageBullet', {
				text: 'When your friends download the Source app, they can use your hotspot for free without passwords.',
				imageSource: '/assets/become-a-host/heart.svg',
				imageAlt: 'a heart',
			})%>
		</div>
		<div class="hidden-small-screens large-screen-dashboard">
			<img src="/assets/become-a-host/dashboard_view_full.png" alt="The Source admin panel" />			
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bottom-buttons">
		<div class="heading-container">
			<h2 class="thin">
				For every router purchased, a router is distributed to someone in need.
			</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="button-container">
			<!-- TODO (dillchen): point these to the right places -->
			<a href="/buy" class="button blue-button">Buy Source Router</a>
			<a href="/learn-more" class="button blue-button white-button">Learn more</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<%- include('../partials/footer', { background: 'white' }) %>
